00:33:37,030 --> 00:33:37,870
Cuicui,

572
00:33:37,880 --> 00:33:39,980
I will find a way to take you with us.

573
00:33:48,200 --> 00:33:49,040
Let's go.

574
00:33:51,160 --> 00:33:52,820
But now Cuicui is asleep.

575
00:33:53,070 --> 00:33:54,830
