what if we get lost?

576
00:33:54,830 --> 00:33:57,000
Just head northward and retrace our steps.

577
00:33:57,000 --> 00:33:58,130
How could we need a little demon?

578
00:33:58,510 --> 00:33:59,350
That's right.

579
00:34:01,680 --> 00:34:02,650
Where is the north?

580
00:34:03,200 --> 00:34:04,780
You can't find the north?

581
00:34:13,110 --> 00:34:15,190
Heavy fog surrounds us.

582
00:34:15,190 --> 00:34:16,720
There are no landmarks either.

583
00:34:16,720 --> 00:34:18,940
Of course I can't give directions.

584
00:34:20,150 --> 00:34:21,210
You're quite proud of that.

585
00:34:21,800 --> 00:34:22,640
Of course I am.

586
00:34:22,960 --> 00:34:25,250
Some people are born tone-deaf.

587
00:34:25,400 --> 00:34:27,130
Some people are born
with no sense of direction.

588
00:34:27,320 --> 00:34:29,550
And some people are born vicious

589
00:34:29,550 --> 00:34:30,500
and clumsy.

590
00:34:34,070 --> 00:34:34,910
Ziqi.

591
00:34:35,590 --> 00:34:36,430
Ziqi.

592
00:34:38,840 --> 00:34:39,680
Ziqi!

593
00:34:42,280 --> 00:34:43,120
Ziqi!

594
00:34:43,960 --> 00:34:44,800
Ziqi!

595
00:34:49,920 --> 00:34:50,760
Ziqi!

596
00:34:53,720 --> 00:34:54,560
So talkative.

597
00:34:54,960 --> 00:34:56,210
Now you know fear?

598
00:34:57,880 --> 00:34:58,760
Where did you go?

599
00:34:58,760 --> 00:34:59,960
You scared me to death.

600
00:34:59,960 --> 00:35:01,840
I thought you had left me again.

601
00:35:01,840 --> 00:35:02,860
Let me go.

602
00:35:03,320 --> 00:35:04,250
No.

603
00:35:04,670 --> 00:35:07,440
