- I won't let go.

604
00:35:07,440 --> 00:35:09,170
- What if you leave me again?
- What are you doing?

605
00:35:11,320 --> 00:35:12,420
This time it won't happen.

606
00:35:13,190 --> 00:35:14,610
I don't believe you. You swear.

607
00:35:14,800 --> 00:35:16,100
Childish.

608
00:35:18,920 --> 00:35:21,690
I, Mu Ziqi, swear to the heavens,

609
00:35:22,070 --> 00:35:23,860
