in the future,

610
00:35:24,470 --> 00:35:25,750
I will definitely turn back to find you,

611
00:35:25,990 --> 00:35:27,280
no matter how far I have to turn back,

612
00:35:27,280 --> 00:35:28,690
no matter how much effort it takes,

613
00:35:29,200 --> 00:35:30,690
I will definitely find you
and bring you back.

614
00:35:31,760 --> 00:35:32,730
Is that okay?

615
00:35:34,470 --> 00:35:35,810
That's more like it.

616
00:35:36,720 --> 00:35:37,610
Troublesome.

617
00:35:40,510 --> 00:35:42,440
- What are you doing?
- The fog is too thick.

618
00:35:42,440 --> 00:35:43,920
Let me hold your clothes and walk.

619
00:35:43,920 --> 00:35:45,670
